==== CPU ==== 

 Compilation 
 -----------

 $ mkdir build.xeon
 $ cd build.xeon
 $ cmake .. -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../cmake/cmake_template.cmake.Xeon
 $ make
 $ mkdir data

 Execution
 ---------

 $ mpiexec -n 4 exec/iPic3D ../inputfiles/GEM.inp


==== Xeon Phi ==== 

 Compilation 
 -----------

 $ mkdir build.xeonphi
 $ cd build.xeonphi
 $ cmake .. -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../cmake/cmake_template.cmake.XeonPhi
 $ make
 $ mkdir data
 
 Execution
 ---------
 
 $ mpiexec -n 4 exec/iPic3D ../inputfiles/GEM.inp
